snippet: With his 12th win, Darcy Kuemper, who had 29 saves, set a Minnesota record for a rookie. The Rangers lost their second straight.
abstract: Minnesota Wild defeat New York Rangers, 2-1.
lead_paragraph: With his 12th win, Darcy Kuemper, who had 29 saves, set a Minnesota record for a rookie. The Rangers lost their second straight.

headline.main: Wild Edge Rangers as Kuemper Breaks Team Record
